column5: I'm heading up to Kipawa in a couple of weeks and was wondering if anyone had any reports on the fishing, and if the walleye have started or finished spawning yet. any info would be greatly appreiciated. thanks in advanced. Doug.

hi Doug just got back from red pine chute area its part of lake Kipawa..the fishing was good limited out the first day in there were three of us in the boat ...i dont think the bigger fish were biting when we were there the biggest we got was 4lbs..the season a little later this year so you should be alright so good luck on your trip
